    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is suitable for someone looking for a functional car at a more accessible price point. While the engine and transmission are operational, the car shows noticeable signs of age, including some exterior blemishes and interior wear. It has been a reliable driver, though it may require some minor maintenance and cosmetic attention in the near future to keep it in peak shape. It is a solid choice for a daily commuter if you don't mind a few imperfections.",
