    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car performs perfectly; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and all electronic features and climate controls function exactly as they did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
