    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, an exemplary model that balances sophisticated performance with exceptional value. This unit has been meticulously maintained and subjected to a comprehensive professional inspection to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Offering a refined driving experience and a commanding road presence, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a reliable, high-caliber automobile.",
